  "6": {
    "inputs": {
      "text": "A cinematic medium shot, low angle with slight upward tilt, of a slim, angular ten-year-old boy seated atop a flat, pale grey granite (#A9A9A9) stone that juts out over the edge of a wide, still freshwater pond like a natural bench, its surface worn satin-smooth from years of use, sage-green (#8A9A5B) and burnt-orange (#CC5500) lichen clinging to its underside and visible edges. Golden hour afternoon sunlight (#FFB347) bathes the scene in warm amber tones, casting dappled emerald shadows from the enormous canopy of a massive ancient banyan tree with elephant-grey (#848484) bark draped in emerald moss (#2E8B57), its aerial roots descending behind the stone toward the water. The boy, Arjun, is small for his age at roughly four-foot-six, with medium-brown skin (#8D5524) glowing with warm honey undertones in the golden light, messy black hair (#1A1A1A) with blue-black highlights falling in uneven tufts forward across his forehead, large expressive dark brown eyes (#3B1F0B) framed by thick lashes gazing downward with a soft contemplative quality, a small dark brown mole (#2B1B0E) on his left cheek, thin angular frame with visible shoulder blades and knobby knees. He wears a faded blue shirt (#7B9BAF) — once vivid cobalt, now washed pale and salt-stained — hanging loose and bunching slightly at his thin waist, and frayed khaki-brown shorts (#8B7355) ending above the knees, resting against the grey stone surface. His bare feet with slightly splayed toes and dusty soles press flat against the warm granite, his knees drawn up loosely with thin arms resting on them, his right hand curled around the stone's familiar grip-point where faint wear-marks show habitual use. His mouth is neutral, jaw relaxed, brow smooth, eyes downcast and half-lidded in quiet contemplation. Below the stone's edge, the tawny-gold (#D4A437) translucent shallows of the pond reveal smooth pebbles on the bottom, with a faint distorted reflection of the boy's silhouette rippling on the still water surface, jade-green (#3B7A57) lotus pads floating nearby with mercury-like droplets. Pixar-style 3D, soft global illumination, polished cinematic quality. Color palette of warm amber (#FFB347), pale grey granite (#A9A9A9), faded blue (#7B9BAF), tawny gold (#D4A437), emerald green (#2E8B57), and medium brown (#8D5524).",
